    <h3 class="hed">No, the Coronavirus Will Not Change the Global Order</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">We should be skeptical toward claims that the pandemic changes everything. China won’t benefit, and the United States will remain preeminent.</p>
